Requirements:
Install Anaconda3

For Linux distros:

Install
```

Anaconda3-2022.05-Linux-x86_64.sh

```

For Windows download the .exe and follow the install instructions from here:

```

https://docs.anaconda.com/anaconda/install/windows/

```

For MacOS download the installer and follow the instructions from here:

```

https://docs.anaconda.com/anaconda/install/mac-os/

```

Initialize conda

```

conda init

```

Create a venv

```

conda create -n kalman python=3.9

```

Activate the venv

```

conda activate kalman

```

Install the requirements

```

pip install -r requirements.txt

```

Run sim.py

```
python sim.py

```

